Optimize Data Extraction by Excluding Rows in Tabular Data
Exclude rows during table extraction that you do not need to save by using the new Skip record option in the Intelligent Form Reader. Gain better control over the extraction process to capture only the relevant information.

Get Intelligent Form Reader to easily extract unstructured content and tables from documents, excluding rows you need not save.
